    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create independent body for Special Allocation Scheme complaints & safeguarding",
        "additional_details": "We believe that having to complain to your SAS service provider in the first instance can create a conflict of interest, delay action, reduce accountability, and can leave patients at risk. We think that independent review would improve safety, fairness, transparency.",
        "background": "Create an independent body to handle all complaints and safeguarding concerns involving patients on the NHS Special Allocation Scheme.",
